parameters:
Thank you for downloading Ayako-san's Demo
Version. Allow me to explain about the demo
version.

You can play up to the second stage of H-level.
The content and illustrations of various events
may be subject to change. There is a possibility
that bugs may still remain.
That's all for now. Please enjoy!
Would you like to watch the opening?

The protagonist of this story,\c[6]Ayako
Nagatsuki\c[0] (永辻 綾子), divorced due to their
spouse's infidelity and moved to this town with
their beloved child...

One day, suddenly my child collapsed... We went to
various hospitals for examinations, but the cause
was unknown...

While I was at a loss, an old woman suggested that
I visit the shrine...

There, I encountered a mysterious ghost who
claimed to be a guardian spirit. It was revealed
that the cause of my son's collapse was due to the
decline in the guardian spirit's power and the
subsequent invasion of negative energy.

The mysterious ghost introduced themselves
as\c[1]Rei\c[0]... According to\c[1]Rei\c[0], if
they can regain the people's faith, their power
will be restored and they can heal Ayako's son.
Ayako decides to cooperate.

However, the method proposed by\c[1]Rei\c[0] was
to use their own body to seduce men and gather
faith...

Ayako is confused, but she succeeds in regaining
faith in her own way...

And from here on... it was the beginning of
Ayako's frantic journey...
